{% call band.output("Best practices") -%}
<p>Don’t use more than three Calls to action in a row because too many choices will make it hard for users to decide which link to select.</p>
<img src="/assets/cta/cta-bp-over-3.png">

<p>Don’t use multiple Primary styles in the same area, that style is reserved to represent the one most important link.</p>
<img src="/assets/cta/cta-bp-multiple-primary.png">

<p>Don’t stretch the other styles to fit a container or a grid. Only the Brick styles can stretch, otherwise the label padding stays the same in all other styles.</p>
<img src="/assets/cta/cta-bp-stretch.png">
